<div class="wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img src="https://oceangroveslsccom.files.wordpress.com/2020/08/screen-shot-2020-08-25-at-3.25.06-pm.png?w=750" alt="" class="wp-image-546" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content"><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Content\u2026","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":16}}} -->
<p style="font-size:16px;">The OGSLSC Nippers Program is perfect for those aged 7-13 who enjoy the beach. It is a good way to make new friends, keep fit and learn new skills. This club runs a fun and active Nippers program that has two different options for children over 7 years of age. Surf Ed and Surf Sport. The most important part of the Ocean Grove Nippers program is having fun at the beach with your family and friends.<br>Become a member to join. Members aged 7-13 are automatically enrolled inn Surf Ed. Those who choose to participate in Surf Sport pay a $30 levy for the season, which goes towards maintenance of Nipper trailer, marquees etc.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:media-text -->

